pattern_author.notes:
I am 53, married, no children
I am interested in herbalism, archaeology, art quilting, collage, crochet and knitting (and any other hand art that comes within 3 feet of me). I recently began spinning, too :-} 
Since acquiring an electric wheelchair, my boundaries have expanded and I am able to get out and about with my camera again. 
As I live in Michigan,I have the perfect climate for wearing my knits 3/4s of the year :-} 
I am building a small business with my pattern-writing. 
I love designing, and get a thrill whenever I see something made from one of my patterns.

users.about_me:
I am 58, married, no children, two cats, one dog.
I am interested in herbalism, archaeology, art quilting, collage, painting,  jewelry design, crochet and knitting (and any other hand art that comes within 3 feet of me). I recently began spinning, too :-}
As I live in Michigan, it also gives me a great venue for wearing my knits 3/4s of the year :-}
I am building a small business with my pattern-writing.
I love designing, and get a thrill whenever I see something made from one of my patterns. I have a feeling that will continue to be a source of joy. :-}
One of my favorite things to do is make warm things for local homeless folks.
